We have used it for 3+ years and like it.  One adaptation that worked
for us was to take their little chalkboard method to a larger scale at
first.  Our easle has a chalkboard on one side.  I put a smiley face
sticker on the top left corner of the frame for the starting corner.
We made one very large letter at a time.  After learning to make the
letters with the full arm motion, it seemed easier to progress to
making smaller ones.

--Betsy
